title: MAX ROACH PART-2
description:
An exclusive interview with percussionist, Max Roach. This interview was done by Visual artist, Jomo Cheatham in chicago, Illinois on 30 May 1993. Max was appearing in Chicago at the Jazz Showcase, which was located in the Blackstone Hotel and has since moved. This interview is about an hour long but has been edited into several episodes.   Max Roach made his transition on 16 August 2007.
